      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal test-sample statistical characterization not required at MRL 2. Three independent bench replicates performed at each operating point using the same pump unit; coefficient of variation in NIH across replicates < 4%. Sample adequacy judged sufficient for MRL 2 purposes."
